Acceptance: Build one reusable action framework that resolves target, actor mode, typed inputs, policy and authority into a redacted revision-bound preview; fresh confirmation applies exactly once, emits a durable receipt, and exposes correlation for webhook reconciliation. Expiry, replay, target/actor/policy change, stale state, cancellation, retry, and provider failure fail closed. Action families and rollout gates are separate tasks. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.